Kia ora Raffaella,
We hope your week is going well.
Just following up to check whether you=E2=80=99ve been able to access the l=
ink to your privacy request. Please let us know if you=E2=80=99ve encounter=
ed any issues or need further assistance.
[cid:image001.png@01DC28B0.F9F57340]
Privacy Team
Level 5, 136 Fanshawe Street,
PO Box 90347, Auckland 1142
