<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">Kia ora Raffaella,<o:p></o:p></sp=
an></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">Thank you for your email, and ple=
ase accept our sincere apologies for this incident.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">We really appreciate you bringing=
 this to our attention so promptly. We take customer privacy extremely seri=
ously, and we=E2=80=99ve acted quickly to contain
 the matter.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">We can confirm that no one other =
than your email address accessed your folder. Based on our current assessme=
nt, it appears that only you could have
 entered the file in error, and no information has been exposed. To ensure =
security, we=E2=80=99ve deleted both folders and created new ones in ShareF=
ile with secure links. We=E2=80=99ve also notified the Office of the Privac=
y Commissioner and initiated an investigation to
 understand the root cause.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">Additionally, we=E2=80=99ve asked=
 the team to review your request thoroughly to ensure nothing has been miss=
ed and to provide clarity around the redaction
 of information. We will get back to you within 5 workdays.<o:p></o:p></spa=
n></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">Please use the new link below to =
access your folder. You=E2=80=99ll need to enter your email address, first =
name, and surname. You can leave the =E2=80=9CCompany=E2=80=9D
 field blank.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-language=
:EN-US"><a href=3D"https://towernz.sharefile.com/d-s9e40baa94ab04100a6fbeeb=
731e237e7">https://towernz.sharefile.com/d-s9e40baa94ab04100a6fbeeb731e237e=
7</a><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-language=
:EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-language=
:EN-US">Please let me know if you have any problems accessing your folder.<=
o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-language=
:EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;mso-fareast-language=
:EN-US">Warm regards<o:p></o:p></span></p>
