<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-line-height-alt:.75pt"><span style=3D"f=
ont-size:1.0pt;color:white">Kia ora, Tower team, I=E2=80=99m hoping you can=
 help me straighten something out. Back on 1 July 2025 I asked for a full c=
opy of my claim files for C90306048 and C90306256.
 Since then, I=E2=80=99ve received a couple of broken ShareFile links and, =
only just<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-line-height-alt:.75pt"><span style=3D"f=
ont-size:1.0pt;color:white"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">Kia ora, Tower tea=
m,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">I=E2=80=99m hoping=
 you can help me straighten something out. Back on 1 July 2025 I asked for =
a full copy of my claim files for C90306048 and
 C90306256. Since then, I=E2=80=99ve received a couple of broken ShareFile =
links and, only just now, a working link with a small bundle of six documen=
ts.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">I may be misunders=
tanding, but I expected a broader set of records. A few things have left me=
 unsure:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-=
alt:auto;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">Mixed folders =E2=80=93 Onc=
e I finally received a working link, it showed both a folder with my name a=
nd another customer=E2=80=99s name. I=E2=80=99m not sure whether that was i=
ntentional or a display error, but it made me nervous that I
 might be seeing things I shouldn=E2=80=99t=E2=80=94or that others could se=
e mine (see attached screenshot). It seems to be a security and privacy iss=
ue. Could you please confirm (a) what occurred, (b) what records were expos=
ed, (c) the containment steps taken. Also I believe
 you might have make a notifiable privacy breach report to the Office of th=
e Privacy Commissioner and notify the impacted individuals as required<o:p>=
</o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;=
mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">Scope/quantity =E2=80=93 Th=
e six documents look like only a tiny part of the total timeline and scope.=
 I was expecting, to cover the full period not just the very beginning and =
I was expecting the full claim diary/notes,
 internal emails, instructions to contractors, quotes/scopes/variations, si=
te photos/videos, test results (e.g., moisture/soot/asbestos), call recordi=
ngs/transcripts, texts, messages, any engineering or builder assessments, a=
nd third=E2=80=91party correspondence<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"Ms=
oNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-li=
st:l0 level1 lfo3">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">Redactions =E2=80=93 A lot =
of blacking=E2=80=91out appears to cover more than just other people=E2=80=
=99s names/contact details. If there are parts you really do need to withho=
ld, could you please provide a short note explaining the reason
 for each redaction?<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">Could you help me =
with the following so I can get back on track?<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-=
alt:auto;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo6">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">Full file (securely): Pleas=
e resend the complete claim files for both claims via a secure method (encr=
ypted link or hard copy).<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" sty=
le=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l3 level1=
 lfo6">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">Simple document index: A si=
ngle list of everything held on the file (date, author, short description) =
so I can confirm I=E2=80=99ve received the lot.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li c=
lass=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:a=
uto;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo6">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">Redaction reasons: Where so=
mething truly can=E2=80=99t be provided, a short reason and, if possible, a=
 partially released copy with only the sensitive bits removed.<o:p></o:p></=
span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-marg=
in-bottom-alt:auto;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo6">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">ShareFile clarity: Confirma=
tion of (a) what occurred, (b) what records were exposed, (c) containment s=
teps taken, and (d) confirmation that a notifiable privacy breach report ha=
s been made to the Office of the Privacy
 Commissioner and impacted individuals notified, with the reference number =
or clarification why this was not done<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"M=
soNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-l=
ist:l3 level1 lfo6">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">Call recordings/transcripts=
 &amp; communications: Please include any call recordings or transcripts, t=
ext/SMS or instant messages, video calls, any other forms of communication,=
 and notes from face=E2=80=91to=E2=80=91face meetings.<o:p></o:p></span></l=
i></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">Given I asked for =
my full file on 1 July 2025 and again on 28 August 2025, and I still haven=
=E2=80=99t received the complete material =E2=80=93 just
 a very tiny part - could you please share the full files immediately?<o:p>=
</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">Important housekee=
ping: I=E2=80=99d be grateful if you could please preserve all claim record=
s (including emails, texts, photos, task logs, and
 any contractor files) while this is sorted.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
lt:auto"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:12.0pt">Thank you very muc=
h for helping me get clarity. I really appreciate it.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-a=
